<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>문의 내역 목록 (테스트)</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/common.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/user/user_service/style_check_inquiry.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <% if (user && user.role === 'S') { %>
    <%- include('../../partials/user_partials/nav_senior') %>
    <% } else { %>
  <%- include('../../partials/user_partials/nav_index') %>
  <% } %>

<main class="inquiry-container">

  <div class="table-responsive">
    <table class="inquiry-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="width: 15%;">유형</th>
          <th style="width: 50%;">제목</th>
          <th style="width: 15%;">상태</th>
          <th style="width: 20%;">작성일</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr onclick="location.href='/user/user_service/inquiry'" style="cursor: pointer;">
          <td><span class="type-badge">기술문의</span></td>
          <td class="inquiry-title-cell">스마트 약상자 와이파이 연결이 자꾸 끊어집니다.</td>
          <td>
            <span class="status-badge status-답변완료">답변완료</span>
          </td>
          <td>2026. 07. 02.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr onclick="location.href='/user/user_service/inquiry'" style="cursor: pointer;">
          <td><span class="type-badge">배송문의</span></td>
          <td class="inquiry-title-cell">추가 약통 세트 배송 주소를 변경하고 싶습니다.</td>
          <td>
            <span class="status-badge status-답변대기">답변대기</span>
          </td>
          <td>2026. 07. 01.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr onclick="location.href='/user/user_service/inquiry'" style="cursor: pointer;">
          <td><span class="type-badge">서비스문의</span></td>
          <td class="inquiry-title-cell">부모님 계정과 제 계정을 연동하는 방법이 궁금합니다.</td>
          <td>
            <span class="status-badge status-답변완료">답변완료</span>
          </td>
          <td>2026. 06. 28.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</main>


<footer class="footer">
  © 2025 <span>복약안심서비스</span> | Team Jetson5 | 스마트 약상자 기반 복약 관리 플랫폼
</footer>
</body>
</html>